# Summary
This documentation details the Extole destination integration with Amplitude, enabling businesses to stream user behavior data to power customer-led growth initiatives like referral programs and challenges. The integration requires mapping Amplitude user_id to Extole email addresses, supports event filtering, and allows Extole to use Amplitude events for triggering emails, fulfilling rewards, and creating audiences.

